=========Component digram========================================
@startuml

[Build To Order] --> [Prepared Item] 
[Prepared Item] -> [Recipe Management System]
[Recipe Management System] --> [WorkOrder] :Build Instruction
[WorkOrder] --> [Kitchen System\n <WorkCell>] :Send build instruction
[Kitchen System\n <WorkCell>]-> [Kitchen Expeditor Screen] :Display

@enduml

==========Sequence Digram============================================

OMS-->Order-->Schedule-->WorkOrder (Workorder create)-->Workcell(WorkOrder completed)-->Release-->Delivery


@startuml
actor OMS
activate OMS
OMS -> Build_To_Order 
  activate Build_To_Order
    Build_To_Order ->Schedule
	activate Schedule
	Schedule -> WorkOrder: <<Prepare product>>
	activate WorkOrder
	WorkOrder --> Recipe_Management_System :Request for Instruction	
	activate Recipe_Management_System
	Recipe_Management_System --> WorkOrder : receive build instruction
	WorkOrder -> Workcell: Send build instruction        
          activate Workcell
          Workcell -> Expeditor_Screen: display
		  activate Expeditor_Screen          		    
				deactivate Expeditor_Screen			 
			 deactivate Workcell
			 deactivate Recipe_Management_System
             deactivate WorkOrder 
          deactivate Schedule		  
	    deactivate Build_To_Order
      deactivate OMS 	
@enduml